descriptionHtml:
Yes, Its Over Powered, some people like to be a tank, if you dont like it, dont download it.

Comes with:

- Complete Nightingale Armor with over powered stats.
- Blade of Woe that insta kills everything.
- Hidden Treasure (Note Explaining it)

Install Instructions:

Use NMM or Dump the contents into your data folder, ensure \"SuperAlpacca - ReaperOfTheNightmod.esp\" is checked upon start up.

uninstall instructions:

Delete all files related to this mod.
